data.description: Your cozy home awaits! This home is located in a great community with privacy and space to enjoy, the home has an open floor concept with updates. this home is located in the heart of Bethlehem, where you have access to great shopping and restaurants. Near Gwinnett County schools and easy access to the major highways. The home is a level 1 story home, with a 1 master room private, with a vaulted ceiling and 2 additional rooms, a total of 3 spacious bedrooms. There 2 full Bath, the master bath features a double vanity, and a garden tub with a separate shower and a large walk-in closet. The kitchen has an open concept and a breakfast bar. The home is privaged with a landscape area, excellent for garden or adding to current greenery. The backyard is a more private area with a patio, great for gatherings or a relaxing area.
